06:30.720 --> 06:32.400
contract.

06:32.400 --> 06:36.720
It was some all in one provider and you could recognize it from the box, it was an all in

06:36.720 --> 06:40.920
one box, it was a TV, telephony and internet.

06:40.920 --> 06:47.160
